<B>__{two large canvas trucks}
<A>__{barrelling along the mountain path. kezure, the pirate king, leaps from the side of the path, between the two trucks. kezure climbs onto the rear bumper of the first truck. the driver of the second truck spots kezure. he begins to fire shots at the pirate king. as bullets whiz by him, kezure hurriedly removes a thick metal chain from around his neck. he securely connects the two truck bumpers with the chain.}
